bilingual.source: A satisfied consumer is likely to return for more purchases.
bilingual.target: 满意的消费者可能会再次购买。

bilingual.source: The majeure challenge was to find a solution that satisfied everyone.
bilingual.target: 重要的挑战是找到一个让每个人都满意的解决方案。

bilingual.source: The general election night, let me satisfied!
bilingual.target: 晚上的竞选总体还是让我满意的！

bilingual.source: He began to smoke his pipe with a satisfied air
bilingual.target: 他带着满意的神情抽起烟袋来。

bilingual.source: He began to smoke his pipe with a satisfied air.
bilingual.target: 他带着满意的神情抽起烟袋来.

bilingual.source: A satisfied Zeritsky client was a silent client.
bilingual.target: 一个满意的择瑞特斯盖顾客是一个沉默的顾客.

bilingual.source: Is it OK ( good, guaranteed, satisfied, passed )?
bilingual.target: 那是正确的 ( 好的 、 保证的 、 满意的 、 合格的 ) 吗 ?

bilingual.source: A single process is enough to get satisfied result.
bilingual.target: 一个过程就足以令人得到令人满意的结果了。

bilingual.source: A satisfied result has been obtained at different PRF.
bilingual.target: 在不同脉冲重复频率下进行仿真,取得了满意的效果.

bilingual.source: We get a satisfied result through the experimentation.
bilingual.target: 通过实验得到了较为满意的识别结果。

list.abstract: 《Satisfied》是美国歌手Jewel演唱的歌曲。收录在Jewel 2006年6月发行的专辑《Sweet And Wild》中。
基本信息歌名：Satisfied歌手：Tom Waits专辑：Bad As Me(2011)吉他：Tom Waits，Keith Richards，Marc Ribot贝斯：Les Claypool打击乐器：Gino Robair架子鼓：Casey Waits萨克斯：Clint Maedgen口琴：Charlie Musselwhite键盘：Patrick Warren

yingyinNormal.en: I'm satisfied with my care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我满意你的照顾。

yingyinNormal.en: Fine, I'm satisfied with my...
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我很满意你的...

yingyinNormal.en: Are you satisfied with your care?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你对我的照顾满意么？

yingyinNormal.en: Satisfied? Oh, yeah, now I smell him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 满意了吧？对，我现在闻到他了。

yingyinNormal.en: Well then, I'm satisfied with my care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那好吧，我很满意你的照顾。

yingyinNormal.en: Other people are satisfied with staying where they are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他人则安于现状。

yingyinNormal.en: It says to call this number if you're not completely satisfied with this candy bar. Well, I'm not completely satisfied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上面说不满意这条巧克力糖可以拨这个号码，我并不满意。

yingyinNormal.en: Our only way off this island and now it's in pieces. Satisfied?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们唯一离开这个岛的方法已经摔碎了，你满意了？

yingyinNormal.en: Are you satisfied with your care? Please, No. I can't lose you too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你对我的照顾满意么？求你了，不要，我不能再失去你了。

yingyinNormal.en: You're right. I'm not. Now are you satisfied? No. Just disappointed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的对，我不是，现在你满意了吗？不！我只是觉得失望。

yingyinNormal.en: I can not deactivate until you say: You are satisfied with your care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 直到你说你满意我的照顾，我才可以结束工作。

yingyinNormal.en: I can not deactivate until you say: You are satisfied with your care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 直到你说：我很满意你的照顾，我才会结束工作。

yingyinNormal.en: I can not deactivate until you say: You are satisfied with your care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说"我对治疗很满意"，我才能解除任务。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi, Sheldon. Good morning, Dr. Stephanie. I trust Leonard satisfied you sexually last night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，早上好。斯蒂芬妮医生，我想莱纳德昨晚肯定让你性福了吧。

yingyinNormal.en: You're gonna help so many people buddy, so many. That's all for now. I am satisfied with my care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你会帮助很多人的，老兄，超级多。先这样吧，我很满意你的照顾。

yingyinNormal.en: I see you're also a customer. Are you satisfied with our product? She's very realistic. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我了解到你也是我们公司的顾客。对我们的产品满意么？很是逼真。谢谢你们的产品。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, he was happy to be playing for his hometown team, but we weren't satisfied with just being in the NBA.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道，他很开心能为自己家乡的球队效力，但是，我们并不满足于只是进入NBA

yingyinNormal.en: Not your firm. You. We would only ask that this complaint be quashed until the court's jurisdiction is satisfied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是你们律所，是你。我们只有请求，撤消此项申诉直到这个法庭具备受理诉讼的管辖权吧。

yingyinNormal.en: In what way are you screwed? All I want to do is present you as my boyfriend to my mother so she'll be satisfied that I'm in a relationship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁说你完蛋了？我只是想把你当作男友介绍给我妈，让她相信我在恋爱，好让她放心。

yingyinNormal.en: I've come to realize that success is not a matter of attaining one's goals. I've found that when I reached each new higher level of success, I rarely remained satisfied.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意识到成功不是达到目标。每当我达到一个新高度的成功，我很少感到满足。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
